name: Magick Pain Lotion/Body Butter 1.5 oz
description:
Only the finest ingredients are put in our Pain Lotion.  They include Aloe Vera, Avocado Oil, Jojoba Oil, Glycerin, Vitamin E, Vitamin A, Wheat Germ Oil, Carrot Seed Oil, Rosemary, Citric Acid, Witch Hazel, Zinc Oxide, Mineral Powder, Cayenne, Emu Oil, and Potassium Sorbate. To use the pain lotion, apply to affected area after cleansing.  Let absorb into the skin before covering.  You may feel a warming sensation to the area.  Can take up to ½ hr to feel the full effect.

   I combine shipping to the same location.

   Items will be sent once payments have been received.
